author: Mishaal Rahman
title: Official TWRP Available for the Xiaomi Redmi Note 3 (Kenzo/Kate)
text: No longer will Redmi Note 3 and Redmi Note 3 Special Edition users have to worry about figuring out which version of TWRP to flash, as XDA Recognized Developer TheStrix has posted an official, unified version of the popular custom recovery that works on both the kenzo and kate models of the Redmi Note 3.
